Jquery Plugin smoothZone

Summary:

	smoothZone is a tool for items slide show.  you can easily use it to display your items smoothly.
Also we supply many effect that you can choose, like fade, slice.  

Download:
	The current respository is controlled by github. so if you wanna download the current version of this plugin, please visit https://github.com/luoqi1987425/smoothZone for downloading.



Example:

	<div class="container">
		<div>Item 1</div>
		<div>Item 2</div>
		<div>Item 3</div>
		<div>Item 4</div>
	</div>


	$(".container").smoothzone({
		number 		: 2,
		speed	  : 5000,
		effect    : "fade",
		mode	  : "circle"
	});

Source Code Structure:

	i put all the source code in src folder. i put different part into seperated js file.

-src/

---include.js	

---core.js

---item.js

---display.js

---jquery.js

